<!--
	Nonfunctional subdomains:

		- ask *
		- api		(refused)
		- dev-builds	(refused)
		- tinderbox *

	* Times out


	Mixed content:

		- css on conference, extensions and templates from $self *

		- Images on conference, extensions, templates and encontro from $self *

		- Web bugs on extensions from piwik.documentfoundation.org *

	* Secured by us

-->
